<data key="follow up">Check out these groups, some of which were key supporting Corbyn's takeover of the Labour Party leadership.  See also good article at http://www.businessinsider.fr/uk/momentum-the-inside-story-of-how-jeremy-corbyn-took-control-of-the-labour-party-2016-2/ 

