<node id="47">
<data key="label">Peter Willsman</data>
<data key="role">MP</data>
<data key="follow up">See whether he gets elected, a Momentum candidate, to the NEC in Aug 2018
</data>
<data key="bio &amp; notes">CLP rep on the LP NEC. 
CLP MPs (Constituency Labour Party) were perceived as the more left wing faction in the Labour Party. 

He is a member of Momentum, elected to the NEC in 2016. 

30 Jul 18, Willsman, one of Jeremy Corbyn’s closest allies on Labour’s ruling body, blamed Jewish “Trump fanatics” for “making up” allegations of anti-Semitism in the party at a meeting attended by the Labour leader. See https://www.telegraph.co.uk/politics/2018/07/30/labours-anti-semitism-row-blamed-corbyn-ally-jewish-trump-fanatics/

He also appeared to suggest that examples of anti-Semitism within Labour were being “falsified on social media”. One Jewish Labour MP said his comments “beggar belief”.  See his comments in the Jewish Chronicle https://www.thejc.com/news/uk-news/bombshell-recording-proves-corbyn-ally-blamed-jewish-trump-fantatics-for-false-antisemitism-clai-1.467802 

He is intransigent and the LP is silent about what they may do to discipline him see http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6012477/Pressure-mounts-Jeremy-Corbyn-anti-Semitism-row.html 

Willsman is secretary of the Campaign For Labour Party Democracy group (30 Jul 18) see the report of his anti-Jewish rant at the NEC committee meeting which refused to adopt the full international standards for controlling anti-Semitism  https://www.thejc.com/news/uk-news/bombshell-recording-proves-corbyn-ally-blamed-jewish-trump-fantatics-for-false-antisemitism-clai-1.467802

2 Mar 19, there is no love lost between Peter Willsman or Chris Williamson and Jon Lansman. PW and CW make their names for anti-semitism and JL objects, see https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6762703/Jeremy-Corbyns-party-chief-threatens-Momentums-John-Lansman-key-ally.html?ito=amp_twitter_share-related 
It seems Willsman was furious when Momentum withdraw its support for him in Sep 2018 to be on the NEC. He survived when Chris Williamson came to his rescue urging other members to vote for him. 

31 May 19, Willsman is in trouble again for his anti-semitic views, this time accusing the Israeli Embassy of conniving to make Labour look anti-semitic. Finally, pressure is on Labour to act and they have suspended Willsman. https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7090363/Corbyn-ally-recorded-claiming-Israeli-embassy-manufacturing-anti-Semitism-crisis.html


</data>
