Photo of her at this site... https://order-order.com/people/jayne-fisher/ and in company of Sinn Fein’s Conor Murphy, who was sentenced to five years in prison for possession of explosives with intent to endanger life in 1982 and Sinn Fein MLA Jennifer McCann (below centre left), who served ten years for shooting an RUC police officer. 

She only did about two months on Corbyn's staff before having to move on. One could assume because there was general outrage among all MPs that Corbyn would employ a member of Sinn Fein on his personal staff. 

Is she married or related to Andrew Fisher? No. She is the partner of Mike Hedges, Momentum, taxi driver for Corbyn and member of UNITE, so linked to Len McCluskey. </data>
