<data key="label">Max Shanly</data>
<data key="role">Red Labour </data>
<data key="bio &amp; notes">Joined Alex Craven to develop Red Labour FB social network page, with Ben Sellers. Key to Corbyn's support base. 

26,  a brusque young socialist from Epsom in Surrey, who sits on the Labour Party youth wing’s National Committee. During his time as prominent member of Oxford University Labour Club, Shanly forged links with most of the key figures on Labour’s left. He is not sympathetic to Labour’s moderate MPs

7 Sep 18, https://order-order.com/tag/novara-media/  Top Corbynistas are openly referring to John McDonnell by his IRA nickname “The Quartermaster”. Momentum man Max Shanly called the Shadow Chancellor by his IRA nom de guerre on this week’s Novara Media All The Best podcast. Appearing alongside former Corbyn spokesman Matt Zarb-Cousin, Shanly said:

“I went to John McDonnell’s Alternative Models of Ownership Conference this weekend… it was very interesting, I don’t know how many of you have read the Alternative Models of Ownership report commissioned by The Quartermaster and Rebecca Long-Bailey, but it’s a very good read.”</data>
