<node id="404">
<data key="label">Andrew Murray UNITE</data>
<data key="role">Chief of Staff at UNITE</data>
<data key="follow up">Connections with communist party now?
</data>
<data key="bio &amp; notes">Was Chief of Staff at UNITE and now he is a consultant for Corbyn. 

Recently seconded to Mr Corbyn’s office from Unite, where he was chief of staff, Mr Murray is a long-term ally of the Labour leader who spent years in the British Communist Party and a decade leading the Stop the War Coalition.
He is the son of stockbroker Peter Drummond-Murray of Mastrick, the former Slains Pursuivant, an honorary role firmly embedded in Scottish politics for hundreds of year. His mother was the Hon. Barbara Mary Hope, a daughter of the 2nd Baron Rankeillour, who served as the governor of Madras during the British rule of India. Mr Murray was educated at Worth School, a Benedictine independent boarding school in Sussex. See DT article https://www.telegraph.co.uk/politics/2018/08/23/labours-public-schoolboys-jeremy-corbyn-accused-hypocrisy-calls/

He is reputedly close to Jeremy Corbyn. He was drafted in, clearly with McCluskey's support, to run the 2017 general election campaign. He’s often accused of being a Stalinist, because for decades he wrote for the Morning Star and also the Soviet paper Novosti, but this character trait has served him well in running a well oiled election machine. 
  
He was a founder of Stop the War Coalition and is one of its officers, see http://www.stopwar.org.uk/index.php/about/stop-the-war-patrons-officers-steering-cttee

He is the ex-husband of Susan Michie, another well heeled Marxist. 
see http://www.lbc.co.uk/radio/presenters/iain-dale/100-most-influential-people-on-the-left-iain-dale/

Murray is a member of the Communist Party of Great Britain and long-time defender of miners leader Arthur Scargill.  

His real name is Drummond-Murray and he is from a well off Conservative background with a private education. son of a stockbroker, Peter Drummond-Murray of Mastrick, and a descendant of the Earl of Perth, his mother was the daughter of a Conservative MP.

Read more: http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5483887/The-Communist-toffs-taking-hard-left-Labour-party.html#ixzz59LxUmrT6 

Read more: http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3794817/Secret-summit-wipe-Watson-Corbyn-cabal-plans-political-execution-deputy-leader-Downton-mansion-lorded-TUC-bosses.html#ixzz55y72QE2e 

20 Sep 18, Andrew Murray is furious he hasn't been granted a Houses of Parliament pass, so he can come and go as he likes andblames the "Deep State" for this and for "undermining" Corbyn. See explan at https://www.telegraph.co.uk/politics/2018/09/20/left-wingers-love-conspiracy-theory-distraction-real-reasons/?li_source=LI&amp;li_medium=li-recommendation-widget  

5 Mar 19, Murray complains people are unjustly accusing Corbyn and Labour of anti semitism... https://twitter.com/rosskempsell/status/1102876948496347139

Murray on his anti-Zionist pro-Palestinian bandwagon again: He wrote that the roots of the 9/11 terror attacks lay in “Zionist colonialism” of the Balfour declaration. In a December 2005 article for the Morning Star - unearthed by investigative journalist Iggy Ostanin - Mr Murray suggested that the attacks were a criminal act rather than an act of war. (well, actually he has a point. The scale of the crime does not make it any less a crime or give the perps the benefit of being considered warriors in some way).   https://www.thejc.com/news/uk-news/exclusive-top-corbyn-adviser-andrew-murray-linked-9-11-terror-to-zionist-colonialism-1.484031

Murray sits with Seumas Milne and Dr Kamal El-Helbawy, Chair of the Centre for the Study of Terrorism and former speaker for the Muslim Brotherhood in the West, at a SOAS venue to hear who is a Jew and who isn't, anyway according to Dr El Helbawy.   https://richardmillett.wordpress.com/2012/02/14/muslim-brotherhoods-dr-kamal-el-helbawy-defines-a-jew/

