<data key="follow up">The connections may be with Momentum, McDonnell, Corbyn, McCluskey etc or the consequence of a steering meeting with some or all of these people, but for the moment the connection is shown to Seamus Milne who may be assumed to have a role of influence. 
So, follow up all connections. </data>
<data key="bio &amp; notes">Focal point for anti-government activism within the NHS, particularly the junior doctors' strike which caused the government such pain. 

The connections may be with Momentum, McDonnell, Corbyn, McCluskey etc or the consequence of a steering meeting with some or all of these people, but for the moment the connection is shown to Seamus Milne who may be assumed to have a role of influence. 

https://www.youthdebates.org/t/fact-british-medical-association-is-full-of-hard-left-corbyn-supporters/106094

