<data key="bio &amp; notes">This node gathers together the considerable spread of neo-Marxist-communist activity throughout the educational system. 

Links (Edges) may also connect other Nodes where those links are supported by events. 

But there is also a general link between Education and Momentum which has members in educational establishments and who are as active as they can be. 

This Node Education is also show with links to Corbyn's staff who are reputed to encourage the subversion of young people by post modern neo-Marxist-communist teachings. 

See this extensive list of names associated with post modernism... https://web.archive.org/web/20080120221109/http://users.california.com/~rathbone/names.htm

And info on the works of Michel Foucault at https://web.archive.org/web/20080119120548/http://users.california.com:80/~rathbone/foucau10.htm#subjugated 

17 Jul 19, Labour against Private Schools was launched and triggered more talk about what a Corbyn government would do to the British education system. see https://www.theguardian.com/education/2017/jul/18/national-education-service-labour-fresh-ideas

