<data key="label">Tom Unterrainer</data>
<data key="follow up">Check out people and links..


http://socialistreview.org.uk/issue/february-2018 a book of commentaries "Corbyn’s Campaign" edited by Tom Unterrainer (Spokesman Books, £7.95)
January 25, 2016 Abi Rhodes, Adele Williams, Ben Sellers, Chris Williamson, Christine Shawcroft, Tom Unterrainer</data>
<data key="bio &amp; notes">Heavily involved in Socialist Review site, a seriously radical left Marxist communist publication.

http://socialistreview.org.uk/issue/february-2018 a book of commentaries "Corbyn’s Campaign" edited by Tom Unterrainer (Spokesman Books, £7.95)
January 25, 2016 Abi Rhodes, Adele Williams, Ben Sellers, Chris Williamson, Christine Shawcroft, Tom Unterrainer

Keen marxist communist and activist and pro Corbyn, obsessed with class. see his book http://fiveleavesbookshop.co.uk/tag/tom-unterrainer/ 
Mentions Christine Shawcroft, Adele Williams and a generalised commitment to radical social change.... ie revolution without any sense of responsibility for the consequences.. classic communism.</data>
