Laura Rogers, of Momentum, claimed that Anna Gillett, also of Momentum, had been selected by Momentum HQ “behind closed doors” and “without any vote or discussion within the local Momentum group”. She alleged that senior organisers at Momentum, “told outright lies about alternative candidates”. Gillett was endorsed by Momentum on Friday 12 Jan 18. 
DSel

