She is very anti Steve Walker who runs Skwawkbox because she wants to deselect Maria Eagle MP and Walker who is the Chairman of Eagle's CLP committee won't agree. https://www.theredroar.com/2018/01/awksbox-ii-skwawkbox-blogger-to-be-deselected-by-local-momentum-members/ 

