<data key="bio &amp; notes">A network of extreme and violent people and groups who have, in practice, redefined themselves from anarchists to anti fascists, although they behave exactly like violent fascists. Antifa movements and Anti-Fascist Action networks are radical left wing, often anarchist, extra-parliamentary political movements who describe themselves as anti-fascist. 
They condone violence “in the name of eradicating hatred” 

Anti-fascist means Pro-communist, Pro-Anarchy.  They seem unaware, or at least ignore the fact, that the word fascist comes from the Roman word fascis, a stick or rod, or a bundle of them, fasces (3rd declension) and the word was associated with the Italian National Socialist Party of Mussolini. 
Their tactics of bullying, obstruction, violence, aggression are precisely those used by the bully boys of both the Italian fascisti and the German Brown shirts and Nazis. https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/1506259/Fascist-origins-in-ancient-Rome.html

A UK-based network of independent and grassroots groups working together to defeat "fascism" 
Main website:
https://antifascistnetwork.org/get-involved/
https://en-gb.facebook.com/antifascistnetwork/

Their technique is simple, disrupt all meetings they don't like, using violent attacks if necessary. Classic Brown Shirts. https://antifascistnetwork.org/tag/dywizjon-161/

On March 18, they broke up a peaceful meeting at Kings College London See http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5466359/Several-people-hurt-thugs-shut-FREE-SPEECH-event.html

Searchlight Magazine (“Antifascist” info) is also connected with Antifa. 
www.searchlightmagazine.com/   and the network has connections in Europe and the USA: 

Links in all directions, also with the Hunt Saboteurs
and https://nycantifa.wordpress.com/about-us/ from the NYC Antifa own website, with a long list of other Antifa groups all over the world. 

See this critique of Antifa... http://themillenniumreport.com/2017/09/the-sinister-reality-of-antifa-violence-secrecy-links-to-george-soros-perversion-of-social-justice-causes/  
