<data key="bio &amp; notes">Christie is also active in various causes, including animal rights, environmental protection, and the anti-nuclear power movement and is also a Patron of the Palestine Solidarity Campaign, as well as Reprieve,[38] and CFS/ME charity Action for ME.[39]

Patrons of Palestine Solidarity https://web.archive.org/web/20090302091920/http://www.palestinecampaign.org/Index5b.asp?m_id=1&amp;l1_id=2&amp;l2_id=12

