Not much she doesn't complain about, really. Plus, why does she get invited to Sky News to give vent to her leftwing views. Not sure this is  helpful or representative. 

She is linked to AntifascistactionforGreece FB page https://www.facebook.com/antifascistactionforgreece

She, like Corbyn, is happy to air her ideas on Russian TV, see https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NKI0_nRHRvo
</data>
