<data key="label">Jacques Derrida RIP</data>
<data key="bio &amp; notes">Derrida (1930 - 2004) is the so-called father of neo-Marxist postmodernism, who coined the concept of phallogocentrism which puts the (white) male as dominating the entire capitalist strucdture. 

see https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/derrida/

He taught or spent time at these universities:
University of Paris
École Normale Supérieure
École des Hautes Études en Sciences Sociales
Collège international de philosophie
European Graduate School
University of California, Irvine, where Lyotard also spent time. 

See also this article in the Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy which gives a rundown of postmodernism and at the end a critique of it by Habermas who tore holes in their thinking. https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/postmodernism/#9

and this article in revolvy.com https://www.revolvy.com/main/index.php?s=Postmodernism 

</data>
