71-year-old Mr Ian Bone who founded Class War in 1983 said: “I think that’s brilliant, it just shows that Tories and Labour are all the same and we need to build something much more threatening and radical for the left of Labour. I think think that’s absolutely brilliant that they’ve all come out condemning it.” 

