<data key="label">France Insoumise</data>
<data key="bio &amp; notes">La France Insoumise is the latest version of the French Communist party and led by veteran communist Jean-Luc Melenchon. 

In the 2017, French presidential election, the party did really quite well, polling 18% of the vote in the first round and reaching fourth place behind the Republicans led by François Fillon which polled 19%. 

Melenchon was a speaker at the Sep 2018  for The World Transformed, the Momentum-backed side meetings at the Labour Party conference. see https://labourlist.org/2018/08/the-world-transformed-reveals-full-line-up-ahead-of-labour-conference/  </data>
