<data key="bio &amp; notes">Roy Bentham is angling to get the sitting MP, Luciana Berger, replaced (11 Feb 19) Bentham has close connections to John McDonnell, according to the DT,  https://www.telegraph.co.uk/politics/2019/02/10/exclusive-hard-left-critics-jewish-mp-luciana-berger-have-close/
The Daily Telegraph has learnt that two members of Luciana Berger’s local branch executive  - which last Tuesday agreed to put motions of no confidence in her to a vote - are long standing friends of John McDonnell and Emily Thornberry.
