<data key="label">Extinction Rebellion</data>
<data key="follow up">follow up all the connections with the glitterati and celebs, and politicans. https://www.telegraph.co.uk/politics/2019/07/28/peoples-front-extinction-rebellion-points-deeper-divide-within/

See also Dr Mella in this article. https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7321965/Government-transport-adviser-57-cries-fined-500-Extinction-Rebellion-protests.html

</data>
<data key="bio &amp; notes">This group came to prominence campaigning for the environment in 2019, creating chaos in London by blocking routes and demonstrating in various places simultaneously, blocking traffic and causing considerable disruption. 

They are clearly motivated by radical left ideology. 

https://www.telegraph.co.uk/politics/2019/07/28/peoples-front-extinction-rebellion-points-deeper-divide-within/

