<node id="975">
<data key="label">Dr Steven Mella</data>
<data key="bio &amp; notes">Mella attended Extinction Rebellion protests which blocked London and refused to "move on" when asked to by police. He was fined 500 pounds. https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7321965/Government-transport-adviser-57-cries-fined-500-Extinction-Rebellion-protests.html
The judge added that the right to demonstrate was 'fundamental to a free society' but it must remain 'within the law'.
