<node id="981">
<data key="label">Jewish Voice for Labour (but it's not!)</data>
<data key="bio &amp; notes">JVL was setup in July 2017, "to oppose attempts to widen the definition of anti-semitism beyond its meaning of hostility towards, or discrimination, against, Jews as Jews."

What this seems to mean is that the Labour party want to say they support the Jews... but they don't like Israel and argue that Jews don't have a specific right to a Jewish homeland. 

JVL has affiliated to the influential Campaign for Labour Party Democracy which is run by its Secretary Peter Willsman who has been sacked twice for anti-Semitic behaviour, of which he is wholly unrepentant!

The title JVL suggests support for Jews but has often been criticised as anti-Zionist, notably by Jon Lansman, owner of Momentum, who says "that JVL, by denying or diminishing the problem of antisemitism within the Labour Party, have been part of the problem and not part of the solution".
Lansman said JVL could nevertheless not be considered as part of the Jewish community because its involvement in communal life was minimal.
“For an organisation to be ‘part’ of the Jewish community most of its members individually, or the organisation collectively, must surely actively participate in and contribute to some aspects of the religious, social or cultural life of the community,” he said. “JVL does not meet this test.”
JVL co-chair Jenny Manson’s response to Lansman, saying: “There is increasing concern among our members and supporters about the very negative remarks you make about JVL. Many Jewish Labour Party members, working hard for the election of a Labour government, have felt undermined by your comments.” https://jewishnews.timesofisrael.com/jon-lansman-claims-jewish-voice-for-labour-not-part-of-community/
 
JVL also supported Jackie Walker and Chris Williamson when they were suspended for alleged anti-semitism. See... https://www.jewishvoiceforlabour.org.uk/article/in-defence-of-chris-williamson/
and
https://www.jewishvoiceforlabour.org.uk/article/jewish-support-for-chris-williamson/
Full list of supporters of Williamson at https://drive.google.com/file/d/1q3MkjqLDnLn2Ii5pp7__J-AQ83_aK0NX/view




</data>
